            <title><![CDATA[Trump scraps housing bill signing to pressure Senate GOP on SAVE Act]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/trump-scraps-housing-bill-signing-to-pressure-senate-gop-on-save-act</link>
            <description><![CDATA[President Trump upended plans for a major housing bill, refusing to sign legislation that passed Congress with veto-proof majorities. He's trying to press lawmakers to adopt the voting bill known as the SAVE Act. The tactic is familiar. Earlier this year, the president derailed a bipartisan deal on intelligence and surveillance legislation. Geoff Bennett discussed more with Andrew Desiderio.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 18:55:58 -0400</pubDate>
