            <title><![CDATA[What's in the housing affordability bill that Trump refused to sign]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/whats-in-the-housing-affordability-bill-that-trump-refused-to-sign</link>
            <description><![CDATA[The landmark bipartisan housing bill that President Trump hasn't signed is the most significant overhaul of federal housing policy in decades. It contains no new spending, but it does seek to boost supply by making it cheaper and easier to build across the country. To break down the potential impact, Amna Nawaz discussed more with former HUD Secretary Shaun Donovan.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 18:50:38 -0400</pubDate>
